{"tid":279792,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"39歲女重慶大廈疑遭強姦 警緝30歲米八南亞色魔","createTime":"2017-06-11T14:32:35.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-12T00:32:25.000Z","uid":23479,"like":1,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e2e98f5544a0d15825a83e46dc0d472ea415c280","tid":279792,"uid":23479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T14:32:35.000Z","msg":"【星島日報報道】警方接獲一名22歲男子報案，指39歲女凌晨三時許，在尖沙嘴重慶大廈一單位內遭人襲擊。警方接報到場調查時，女事主聲稱遭強姦，色魔已逃去無蹤。<br />\n<br />\n警方將案件由襲擊案改列為強姦案處理，召救護車將女事主送院檢查，案件由油尖警區刑事調查隊跟進。涉案色魔年約30歲，身高約1.8米，案發時身穿白色上衣及藍色牛仔褲。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/sy/ny/api/res/1.2/6QB5AWXfNTkl3N1MB2blvA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NTAwO2g9NDAwO2lsPXBsYW5l/http://media.zenfs.com/en_us/News/singtao/20170611a144206.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2Fsy%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2F6QB5AWXfNTkl3N1MB2blvA--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NTAwO2g9NDAwO2lsPXBsYW5l%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen_us%2FNews%2Fsingtao%2F20170611a144206.jpg&h=8bca3a64&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"938f9623b95dc9cb34b345d2fd16ec383925600c","tid":279792,"uid":23479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T14:45:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"245f0a94f904eff055b3d2604bd84d83f358b851","tid":279792,"uid":37528,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T14:47:14.000Z","msg":"拎曬d賤種去試葯啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9931c019872b6a1c1c26708a06a5673dce47746","tid":279792,"uid":9385,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T14:49:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>拎曬d賤種去試葯啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n葯你老母"},{"pid":"ca0cebc7a91e61fce0ac69cdfa746d066df8b088","tid":279792,"uid":37733,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T14:50:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>拎曬